object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT
ads.sourcecd,
ads.bestaddr1,
ads.producertypecd,
ads.beststateprovcd,
ads.bestpostalcode,
ads.commercialname,
ads.agencymastercode,
ads.agentcd,
ads.agencycd,
ads.agencyterritory,
ads.agencygroupcd,
ads.statuscd,
ads.statusdt,
ads.bestaddrline1,
ads.bestaddrline2,
ads.bestcity,
ads.systemid,
ads.contacttypecd,
ads.paymentpreferencecd,
apl.producer_id,
apl.agency_code,
(ap.last_name ||
CASE
WHEN ap.suffix IS NOT NULL AND ap.suffix != '' THEN (' ' || ap.suffix || ',')
ELSE ','
end ||  ' ' ||
ap.first_name ||
CASE
WHEN ap.middle_name IS NOT NULL AND ap.middle_name != '' THEN (' ' || ap.middle_name)
ELSE ''
end ||
CASE
WHEN ap.term_flag = 1 THEN ' (TERM''D)'
ELSE ''
END
) AS ProducerName,
apl.gw_producer_id,
str.gw_sales_territory_group_desc AS AgencyTerritoryGroup
FROM
dbo.agents_detail_stg ads
JOIN
bronze.adm_producer_license apl
ON ads.sourcecd = apl.gw_producer_id
AND apl.adm_producer_license_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
JOIN
bronze.adm_producer ap
ON apl.producer_id = ap.id
AND ap.adm_producer_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
LEFT JOIN dbo.salesterritory_ref str
ON ads.agencyterritory = str.gw_sales_territory_desc
where sourcecd='5909-0008';
